ve time"/></td>                       <td><p style="font-size:15px;padding:0px; margin:0px; line-height:20px; color:#494949">                       <strong>Save Time</strong></p>                       <p style="font-size:14px;padding:0px; margin:0px; line-height:20px; color:#494949">  Checkout in under 10 seconds with saved cards and addresses.</p></td>                     </tr>                     <tr>                       <td align="left"><img src="http://i1.sdlcdn.com/static/klikpay/img/rewards.png" alt="rewards"/></td>                       <td><p style="font-size:15px;padding:0px; margin:0px; line-height:20px; color:#494949">                       <strong>Earn Rewards </strong></p>                       <p style="font-size:14px;padding:0px; margin:0px; line-height:20px; color:#494949">  Get goodies for all payments you make via FreeCharge.                       </p></td>                     </tr>                   </table>                   </td>                   </tr>                     <tr>                       <td colspan="2"><p style="font-size:14px;padding:0px; margin:0px; line-height:20px; color:#494949; padding-bottom:5px;padding-left:15px;">Log in to FreeCharge or Snapdeal using your registered email OR mobile number as mentioned below:</p>                       <p style="font-size:14px;padding:0px; margin:0px; line-height:26px; color:#494949; padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:15px;">                           Email: <span style="color:#000;"><strong>$email</strong></span><br>                                                      Mobile:<span style="color:#000;"><strong>$mobile</strong></span></p></td>                     </tr>                   </table></td>               </tr>                              <tr>               <td bgcolor="#ffffff">               <table cellpadding="25" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="600" >               <tr>               <td> <p align="center" style="font-size:15px;padding:0px; margin:0px; line-height:20px;                color:#494949">Pay with FreeCharge at</p>               <p align="center">               <img src="http://i1.sdlcdn.com/static/klikpay/img/freecharge.png" alt="freecharge" style="padding-right:30px"/>               <img src="http://i1.sdlcdn.com/static/klikpay/img/snapdeal.png" alt="snapdeal"/>                              </p>               <p align="center" style="font-size:15px;padding:0px; margin:0px; line-height:20px; color:#494949">And this list is only getting <span style="font-size:17px;">bigger!</span></p></td>               </tr>               </table>                             </td>               </tr>                              <tr>                 <td><p style="font-size:15px;padding:0px; margin:0px; line-height:20px; color:#494949">Lots of Love,<br>                     Team FreeCharge</p></td>               </tr>             </table></td>         </tr>       </table></td>   </tr>   <tr bgcolor="#fbfcfd">  <td><p align="center"  style="padding:0px; margin:0px; padding-top:40px;">Download the FreeCharge app today</p>          <p align="center" style="padding:0px; margin:0px; padding-bottom:40px;padding-top:20px">          <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/in/app/id877495926?mt=8" target="_blank" style="border:0; text-decoration:none;"><img src="http://i1.sdlcdn.com/static/klikpay/img/appstore.png" alt="appstore"/></a> <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.freecharge.android" style="border:0; text-decoration:none;" target="_blank"><img src="http://i1.sdlcdn.com/static/klikpay/img/googlestore.png " alt="googlestore"/></a>           <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/apps/freecharge-recharge-mobile-dth-data-card/9wzdncrdsr94" style="border:0; text-decoration:none;" target="_blank"><img src="http://i1.sdlcdn.com/static/klikpay/img/windowstore.png " alt="windowstore"/></a> </p></td>   </tr>   <tr>
